== Romanian ==
=== Etymology ===
It is generally agreed to be from PIE ''*bhel-'', "to gleam", but there is disagreement whether the word is one of the earliest Romanian loans from [[Old Slavonic]], or whether it is a pre-Roman word. The Romanian word also has an Albanian cognate, ''[[baltë]]''.

===Noun===
'''baltă''' {{f}}, pl. ''[[bălţi]]''
#puddle, pond.
